---
title: Mushroom Cottage Pie with green peas and creamy mash topping
description: This cottage pie is cheesy and topped with potatoes, which sounds pretty great already-but that's not all! There's also the thick, rich tomato sauce featuring charred mushrooms and vibrant green peas that forms the filling of this unmissable veggie dish.
